width="760"
height="395"
loading="lazy" data-zoomable />&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;figcaption>
Snapping Option
&lt;/figcaption>&lt;/figure>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Sau đó bật nút Enable Snapping (hình cái nam châm) ở Snapping Toolbar.&lt;br>
&lt;figure id="figure-snapping-toolbar--enable-snapping">
&lt;div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
&lt;div class="w-100" >&lt;img alt="Ảnh 1" srcset="
